##  Investor Relations 

#  Investor Relations 

**Enstar Group (NASDAQ: ESGR) is a leading global insurance group that provides innovative insurance solutions through our network of group companies. Our diversified portfolio of companies are positioned across the world’s major insurance hubs spanning Bermuda, the US, London, Continental Europe and Australia.**

Our core objective is consistent improvement of net book value per share, a goal we achieve by leveraging of our thorough understanding of risks and liabilities. Enstar has completed more than 120 acquisitions since its predecessor was formed in 1993.
